{"type": "article", "id": 17037, "title": "不插电冰箱", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-04T07:10:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 122, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021355352B01odW8MkfSuKtG.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是荷兰设计师 Floris Schoonderbeek 的不插电冰箱，它其实相当于一个小的地窖。打开上面的门，穿过一个带台阶的通道，就能到达一个直径 2.28 m 的圆球里.里面可以放 500 公斤的食物，相当于 20 个冰箱的容量。这个冰箱专门放在地下，利用土壤的天然的保溫将温度维持在 7℃—15℃ 之间，很有环保的意义。它曾在米兰设计周上展出，预计年底可以上市。 \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144236GqN6lCOR7xoV5DBg.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"715\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.1\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144237kqJeIpd4Kx2N5moW.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"675\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144237gw4RiMymvTY0x7fK.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"460\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70769231\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144238nPhYlJD7cfjvHXK4.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"433\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66615385\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144238kve3fqbKzLDPw69a.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"329\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.50615385\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}